&lt;h4&gt;Extensions.&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;🗄️ &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.virtualosmuseum.org/&#34;&gt;The Virtual OS Museum&lt;/a&gt;, a scant 174 GB install. / Other museums: &lt;a href=&#34;https://plugsocketmuseum.nl/index.html&#34;&gt;Plugs and Sockets&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://plugsocketmuseum.nl/index.html&#34;&gt;Pocket Calculating Devices&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;https://imaginaryinstruments.org/&#34;&gt;Imaginary Musical Instruments&lt;/a&gt;. / &lt;a href=&#34;https://archive.org/details/manualsplus&#34;&gt;Manuals Plus&lt;/a&gt;. (The plus is even more manuals.) / &lt;a href=&#34;https://rip.so/&#34;&gt;rip.so&lt;/a&gt;, the digital graveyard. / 👯‍♀️ &lt;a href=&#34;https://data.post45.org/posts/playboy-fiction-index/&#34;&gt;The Playboy Fiction Index&lt;/a&gt;. / 🛠️ &lt;a href=&#34;https://dirtylittlezine.com/&#34;&gt;Dirty Little Zine&lt;/a&gt;, a free tool for making an 8-page zine. / &lt;a href=&#34;https://audiomass.co/?multitrack=1&#34;&gt;AudioMass&lt;/a&gt;, browser-based multi-track audio editing. / &lt;a href=&#34;https://inobara.com/&#34;&gt;inobara&lt;/a&gt;, simple link saving. / 👀 &lt;a href=&#34;https://wewere.online/&#34;&gt;we were online&lt;/a&gt;. / &lt;a href=&#34;https://eyeball.rory.codes/&#34;&gt;eyeball&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
